data.description:
This 5 bedroom 2 bath single family home located in Westlake is the perfect home for a family. The house has a fresh coat of paint that brightens up the house. Located in Westlake school district and close to shopping and easy access to I-90 and 480. The house is on a large plot of land with a back deck, covered outside area and two sheds, also a large area for a garden. The home has a large two car garage. There is a full unfinished basement with tons of storage and a full size washer and dryer. The kitchen is equipped with a dishwasher, oven stove combo and a refrigerator. This is an opportunity that will not last and you do not want to miss!

Owner pays for water. Tenant is responsible for gas electric and wifi. Last months rent is due at signing. Absolutely no smoking of any kind is permitted. Small dogs under 35lbs are permitted limit one dog. $300 non refundable pet deposit is due at signing.
